title: Elfew 20 Pack Small Activity Books for Kids Ages 4-12 Year Old, Kids Party Bag Fillers, Carnival Prizes, Word Search, Find the Difference, Maze and Search Hidden Object, Goodie Bag Gift Stuffer
features: Rich content：Contains 20 different children's brain game books,a total of 280 different games.Game contain Word Search, Maze, Find the Difference, Dot to Dot and Search Hidden Object.

Learning in Play: Kids enjoy hours of entertainment with a wide variety of brain stimulating activities, and improve your child hand-eye coordination, reading, counting and creativity through playing.
Made of average thickness paper and both sides are available, that great for coloring with crayons, pastels and pencils.
Small Sizes: Small activity books for kids measures 7.1” x 5.1” which are easy to carry around for kids in travel or on a road trip.

Kids Party Favour: These small activity books can be as a present to your child for the party stuffer fillers or birthday goodie bag for boys and girls. Classroom education activity, kids road trips activity and other travel games supplies etc.
